summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Dicer admin panel. Backend APIs mostly functional with one validation issue. Frontend UI and integration working well with minor role selection UX issue.

critical_bugs.issue: Duplicate email validation not working - allows creating users with existing emails
critical_bugs.impact: Can create multiple users with same email (e.g., superadmin@gmail.com)

ui_bugs.issue: Role dropdown selection has selector issues - difficult to select specific roles programmatically

success_percentage: Backend: 92% (11/12 tests passed), Frontend: 95% (19/20 features working)
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix duplicate email validation in backend /api/users endpoint - currently allows creating users with existing emails when it should return 400 error
